==English==
===Noun===
'''cricket''' (''plural'' '''crickets''')

#An insect in the order [[orthoptera]] that makes a [[chirping]] sound by rubbing its [[wing]] [[casing]]s against [[comb]]s on its [[hind leg]]s.

